  "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/questions/53565210/validate-parameter-of-constructor-before-calling-superclass-constructor",
  "title" : "Validate parameter of constructor before calling superclass constructor",
  "body" : "<p>For example, constructor like this : </p>\n\n<pre><code>public class Car extends Vehicle {\n     public Car(Car a){\n         super(a.getName()); //what if 'a' is null \n     }\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>I cannot check condition of parameter before calling super().</p>\n"
}